description: Official government advice against all-non essential travel from Ireland is to remain in place.
title: Coronavirus: Ireland's travel advice extended to 20 July
title_page: Coronavirus: Ireland's travel advice extended to 20 July - BBC News
maintext: The country's health minister said that in the last few months, about 2% of new cases came from international travel and that had "gone up to 17% in the last week".
